| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1586 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 96763cfe-1db2-5fd2-b1e2-f4b97633f093"
